name: MultiplyImageFilter
functor_type: Functor::Mult< typename InputImageType::PixelType, typename InputImageType2::PixelType, typename OutputImageType::PixelType>
detaileddescription:
This class is templated over the types of the two input images and the type of the output image. Numeric conversions (castings) are done by the C++ defaults.
